{"word":"ἀλέα","slug":"ἀλέα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀλέα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>for A., see <a href='S:ἀλέομαι'><el>ἀλέομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li250'><b>A. </b><i>an escape</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>shelter from</i> <el>ὑετοῦ</el> <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li250'><b>B. </b><i>warmth, heat</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b> (<a href='S:derived, derivation'>Deriv.</a> uncertain.)<p/></div>"}]}